						<summary>

						<p>On the lintel of the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the Chennakēśavasvāmin temple. . • • • .</p>						

						<p>Dated in Śaka 1733, <hi rend="italic">Prajōtpatti.</hi></p>						

						<p>States that Nārāyaṇa-reḍḍi, son of Yaram-reḍḍi-Sūrāreḍḍi built the temple. The work was executed by Chennakēśava, son of Rudrābattu of Kannamūru.</p>						

